member.summary:
Gets a list of Carriers for this customer.
if the customer is a shipto it will return the shipto carriers if they have more than 0 carriers, 
if the carrier count is 0 and there is a parent it will return the parents carriers.

Gets a list of Salespersons for this customer.
if the customer is a shipto it will return the shipto Salespersons if they have more than 0 Salespersons, 
if the Salespersons count is 0 and there is a parent it will return the parents Salespersons.

member.example:
var unitOfWork = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<IUnitOfWork>();
var repository = unitOfWork.GetRepository<Category>();
var categoryList = repository.GetTable().Where(x=>x.Active < DateTimeProvider.Current.Now).ToList();

var unitOfWork = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<IUnitOfWork>();
var repository = unitOfWork.GetRepository<Category>();
var category = repository.Get(Guid.NewGuid());

var unitOfWork = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<IUnitOfWork>();
var repository = unitOfWork.GetRepository<Category>();
var category = repository.Get(Guid.NewGuid().ToString());

var unitOfWork = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<IUnitOfWork>();
var repository = unitOfWork.GetRepository<Product>();
var product = ServiceLocator.GetInstance<Product>();
product.Name = test;
repository.Insert(product);
unitOfWork.Save();

var unitOfWork = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<IUnitOfWork>();
var catToDelete = unitOfWork.GetRepository<Category>().Get(Guid.NewGuid());
repository.Delete(catToDelete);
unitOfWork.Save();
